      <title>气候行动计划六年后冰岛将首次亮相绿色环保</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/iceland-to-make-green-debut-six-years-after-climate-action-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在制定气候行动计划六年后，以及以欧元进行银团债务交易三年后，冰岛正计划出售其首次发行的绿色债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/iceland-to-make-green-debut-six-years-after-climate-action-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首席执行官表示，即使在重述后，ADM 激励计划水平仍保持不变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/adm-incentive-plan-levels-hold-even-after-restatements-ceo-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即使阿彻-丹尼尔斯-米德兰公司周二宣布在财务调查后进行数年的内部盈利调整，但与营养部门业绩密切相关的阿彻-丹尼尔斯-米德兰公司高管的薪酬方案仍然有效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-12/adm-incentive-plan-levels-hold-even-after-restatements-ceo-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
